<div class="Gastronomy">
 <h2><font color="#800080">Gastronomy</font></h2>

<p>Our restaurants are diverse, offering a variety of options. From buffet restaurants, which serve dishes from around the world, specialty restaurants that provide a gourmet experience, and themed cuisine restaurants, such as steakhouses, Japanese and Italian restaurants, etc. Everything so that everyone has a unique opportunity to explore flavors.</p>
 
<img src="img/comi1.jpg" alt="cruzeiro" height="380" width="300">
<img src="img/comi3.jpg" alt="cruzeiro" height="380" width="250">
<img src="img/comi2.jpg" alt="cruzeiro" height="380" width="300">


<p><br></p>

<p><strong>Did you know we have cooking classes on board?</strong></p>
    Our cruise offers optional cooking classes with our chef Queren, who is knowledgeable in a variety of cooking styles.
    The chef explains the cooking techniques in English, and provides step-by-step instructions for participants to follow. During classes, students learn to prepare recipes and use different kitchen utensils, to understand vocabulary related to cooking in English.
    The dishes are made in groups, which provides a social and fun experience, so that participants can interact with each other, share tips and exchange culinary experiences.</p>

