   <div class="about the course">
    <h2><font color="#800080">Onboard activities</font></h2>
   
   <p><strong>Get a discount on your next CruiseLear trip</strong></p>
   <p>If you participate in any activity proposed on board, you will earn points, which you can present on your next CruiseLear trip and get a discount, cool isn't it? Activities include:</p>
   <p><strong>ATTENTION: Activities on board are paused during lecture hours</strong></p>
   <p><br></p>
   
   <p><strong>- Sports</strong></p>
   <p>Small areas for practicing sports such as basketball, miniature golf and table tennis, under the supervision of our instructors
   Gyms open from 5:00 am to 7:30 am, and reopen from 11:15 am, there are breaks on lecture days</p>

<p><br></p>

<p><strong>- Educational Casinos</strong></p>
<p>Where you can try your luck <strong>without the use of bets (money)</strong>, in games such as blackjack, poker and slot machines, players can exchange their points collected in games for prizes. Thus providing more safety and fun for our passengers, open all week, starting at 8:00 pm</p>

<p><br></p>

<p><strong>- Cinema</strong></p>

<p><strong>Films only in English and subtitles</strong></p>
<p>Sessions take place from Monday to Friday, from 8:00 pm to 10:30 pm</p>

<p><br></p>

<p><strong>- Activities for children and teenagers</strong></p>
If you have children with you, there are play areas and children's clubs available on our ship. They can be looked after safely, thanks to our tutors present in these spaces, open all week, from 07:30 to 22:00<p>

<p> <br/><br/><br/> </p>

 <div class="Attractions">
 <h2><font color="#800080">Attractions and themed parties</font></h2>
 
 <p>Themed parties are a way to engage with people on board. One of the most talked about on our cruise is the tropical party, where we offer a wide variety of tropical food and drinks. Where passengers wear tropical clothing and accessories, such as swimsuits, floral shirts, Hawaiian necklaces, etc. There are attractions every night, with live music and open bars, for passengers to enjoy.</p>
 
